item.title: With record recruitment drives, 2022 ushered in new hope for Telangana’s youth
item.description: With record recruitment drives, 2022 ushered in new hope for Telangana’s youth The Year 2022 would be remembered for a long time to come as it ushered in a new hope for the unemployed youth and government job aspirants
